# Certifications — Devendra Singh

This repo stores scans/PDFs of my professional certifications, training completions and badges. Each certificate has metadata (issuer, issue date, credential ID, verification link).

How to read entries
- certs/<file>.pdf — Certificate PDF or badge image
- metadata/<file>.yml — YAML with fields: title, issuer, date, credential_id, verification_url, filename

Example entry
- Title: Finite Element Analysis (FEA) — Intermediate
- Issuer: ANSYS Academy
- Date: 2024-05-10
- Credential ID: ANS-123456
- Verification: https://example.com/verify/ANS-123456
- File: certs/ANSYS_FEA_2024.pdf

